dc_title_s: West Indies, Cuba--north coast, Punta Silencio to Bahía Samá (Raster Image)
dc_description_s: Prepared and published by the Defense Mapping Agency. Depths shown by isolines and soundings. Relief shown by contours and spot heights. "From Cuban charts to 1975." "Copyright 1996 by the United States Government. No copyright claimed under Title 17 U.S.C." "Soundings in meters." Inset: Punta Silencio to Punta Guarico. Scale 1:100,000. Includes compilation diagram. Map NO.26244 This map is part of a collection of scanned and georeferenced nautical charts produced by the National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency (NGA).
